# AI API Configuration

# Groq API (PRIMARY - Fast and reliable)
# Get your FREE API key from: https://console.groq.com/keys
# Model: llama-3.3-70b-versatile (Very fast, high quality)
VITE_GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# OpenRouter API (FALLBACK - Free tier available)
# Get your FREE API key from: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# Model: meta-llama/llama-3.2-3b-instruct:free
VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_openrouter_api_key_here

# How it works:
# 1. Primary: Groq API is used for all requests (fast, reliable)
# 2. Retry: If Groq fails, retries up to 2 times (500ms, 1000ms delays)
# 3. Fallback: If Groq still fails, automatically switches to OpenRouter
# 4. Seamless: Users never see errors, conversation history is preserved
